\begin_layout Section*
Takeaway-message
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Anything that makes people feel uncomfortable, there is always a better
 process to help us; 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
A part of the previous knowledge is not only for learning, but also for
 using.
 Learning more broad things, when facing more extensive decisions, can also
 be more or less reflected;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The process of understanding something is gradual, don’t expect to understand
 it completely at once.
 It’s better to be patient.
 
\end_layout

